@startuml elpapi42_deep-deblurring

skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor<<frontend>> #FFFFD0
  BackgroundColor<<backend>> #D0FFD0
  BackgroundColor<<model>> #D0D0FF
  BackgroundColor<<storage>> #FFD0D0
}

[Frontend (Vue.js)] <<frontend>> as Frontend
[Backend (Flask)] <<backend>> as Backend
[Model Serving (TensorFlow Serving)] <<model>> as ModelServing
[Model Repository] <<model>> as ModelRepo
[Cloudinary] <<storage>> as Cloudinary
[Redis] <<storage>> as Redis
[PostgreSQL] <<storage>> as PostgreSQL

Frontend --> Backend : HTTP/REST
Backend --> ModelServing : gRPC
Backend --> Cloudinary : API
Backend --> Redis : Cache/Session
Backend --> PostgreSQL : Data Storage
ModelServing --> ModelRepo : Load Model

@enduml